  "excerpt": "",
  "content": "<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I went out today so I took this chance to play with the new phone's camera. All photos are straight point-n-shoot, no retouch, no editing -- except resize to fit 1200x900px.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5441,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_01.webp\"><img src=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_01-1024x382.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5441\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5442,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_02.webp\"><img src=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_02-1024x382.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5442\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5443,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_03.webp\"><img src=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_03-1024x382.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5443\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5444,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_04.webp\"><img src=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_04-1024x382.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5444\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5445,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_05.webp\"><img src=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_05-1024x382.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5445\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:image {\"id\":5446,\"sizeSlug\":\"large\",\"linkDestination\":\"media\"} -->\n<figure class=\"wp-block-image size-large\"><a href=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_06.webp\"><img src=\"https://macsfvent.sgp1.cdn.digitaloceanspaces.com/media/2022/12/pair_06-1024x382.webp\" alt=\"\" class=\"wp-image-5446\"/></a></figure>\n<!-- /wp:image -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>I like some photos from one phone and some from another. It's all preference.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Anyway. That's all for 2022. Welcome 2023.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Happy New Year. 🎉</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->",
